ce/Emmanuel_Macron\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Yo supported the Zionist regime in its criminal war against the people of Palestine.\", \"from\": 922, \"to\": 1006, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 922, \"end\": 924, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Yo\", \"score\": 0.9999999999940883, \"rank\": 5.8721770780924725e-12, \"text\": \"Yo\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Yo\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Yo\"}, {\"begin\": 939, \"end\": 953, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Zionist_entity\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Zionist regime\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Zionist_entity\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Zionist_entity\"}, {\"begin\": 996, \"end\": 1005, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/State_of_Palestine\", \"score\": 0.9998686429032161, \"rank\": 9.398860222784234e-05, \"text\": \"Palestine\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/State_of_Palestine\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/State_of_Palestine\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"You provided Zionists with weapons, you helped murder our brother and sisters, our children.\", \"from\": 1007, \"to\": 1099, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1020, \"end\": 1028, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Zionism\", \"score\": 0.9999999997630766, \"rank\": 2.367369540031287e-10, \"text\": \"Zionists\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Zionism\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Zionism\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"You invited the Zionists to Olympic games.\", \"from\": 1100, \"to\": 1142, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1116, \"end\": 1124, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Zionism\", \"score\": 0.9999999997630766, \"rank\": 2.367369540031287e-10, \"text\": \"Zionists\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Zionism\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Zionism\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"You will pay for what you have done.\", \"from\": 1143, \"to\": 1179, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Rivers of blood will flow through the streets of Paris.\", \"from\": 1180, \"to\": 1235, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1229, \"end\": 1234, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999965525603, \"rank\": 3.447550122002151e-09, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"This day is approaching.\", \"from\": 1236, \"to\": 1260, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"God willing.\", \"from\": 1261, \"to\": 1273, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Allah is the greatest,\\\" said the Hamas fighter.\", \"from\": 1274, \"to\": 1321, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1307, \"end\": 1312, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hamas\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.8391432387105643e-22, \"text\": \"Hamas\", \"types\": [\"Q7278\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hamas\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hamas\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"According to aNews Xreport, while speculation has arisen about the involvement of Hamas, there is no definitive evidence linking the video to the group, and it has not been shared on official Hamas channels.\", \"from\": 1323, \"to\": 1530, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1405, \"end\": 1410, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hamas\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.8391432387105643e-22, \"text\": \"Hamas\", \"types\": [\"Q7278\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hamas\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hamas\"}, {\"begin\": 1515, \"end\": 1520, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hamas\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.8391432387105643e-22, \"text\": \"Hamas\", \"types\": [\"Q7278\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hamas\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hamas\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The authenticity of the video remains uncertain but has raised concerns regarding security at the Paris Olympics, anticipated to be heavily guarded.\", \"from\": 1532, \"to\": 1680, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"According to anNBC Newsreport, citing researchers at Microsoft, the video of a man purported to be a Hamas fighter threatening the Olympics, is part of a Russian-linked disinformation campaign meant to disrupt the event.\", \"from\": 1682, \"to\": 1902, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1735, \"end\": 1744, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Microsoft\", \"score\": 0.9998925262288784, \"rank\": 0.00010709248106364368, \"text\": \"Microsoft\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Microsoft\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Microsoft\"}, {\"begin\": 1783, \"end\": 1788, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hamas\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.8391432387105643e-22, \"text\": \"Hamas\", \"types\": [\"Q7278\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hamas\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hamas\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Researchers from Microsoft\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s Threat Analysis Center, who reviewed the video, said on Tuesday that\\u00c2\\u00a0a group known as Storm-1516, a small but prolific outgrowth of\\u00c2\\u00a0Russia\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s infamous Internet Research Agency troll farm, appeared to be behind the video.\", \"from\": 1904, \"to\": 2158, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2089, \"end\": 2113, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Internet_Research_Agency\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Internet Research Agency\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Internet_Research_Agency\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Internet_Research_Agency\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The video has in recent days been spread by several popular accounts known to traffic in Russian propaganda, with some also trying to claim it came from Israel, added the report.\", \"from\": 2159, \"to\": 2337, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2248, \"end\": 2266, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Propaganda_in_the_Russian_Federation\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 5.383795300746793e-32, \"text\": \"Russian propaganda\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Propaganda_in_the_Russian_Federation\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Propaganda_in_the_Russian_Federation\"}, {\"begin\": 2312, \"end\": 2318, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Israel\", \"score\": 0.9999997947193362, \"rank\": 2.051344877025533e-07, \"text\": \"Israel\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Israel\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Israel\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"This operation closely aligns with tactics, techniques and procedures observed in previous Storm-1516 operations, including a previous video that similarly pretended to be Hamas,\\\"NBC News quotedMicrosoft group as saying in a statement.\", \"from\": 2339, \"to\": 2575, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2512, \"end\": 2517, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hamas\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.8391432387105643e-22, \"text\": \"Hamas\", \"types\": [\"Q7278\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hamas\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hamas\"}, {\"begin\": 2519, \"end\": 2527, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NBC_News\", \"score\": 0.9999778587916921, \"rank\": 2.2141693293869142e-05, \"text\": \"NBC News\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NBC_News\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NBC_News\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Meanwhile, On Telegram, Hamas official Izzat al-Risheq denied the video had come from Hamas, calling it a forgery.\", \"from\": 2577, \"to\": 2691, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2591, \"end\": 2599, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Telegraphy\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 6.091317657518711e-14, \"text\": \"Telegram\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Telegraphy\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Telegraphy\"}, {\"begin\": 2601, \"end\": 2606, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hamas\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.8391432387105643e-22, \"text\": \"Hamas\", \"types\": [\"Q7278\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hamas\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hamas\"}, {\"begin\": 2663, \"end\": 2668, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hamas\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.8391432387105643e-22, \"text\": \"Hamas\", \"types\": [\"Q7278\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hamas\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hamas\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Previous Olympic events, such as the 1972 Munich Games and the 1996 Atlanta Games, have faced security threats.\", \"from\": 2693, \"to\": 2804, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"With the Paris Olympics opening ceremony just days away, French authorities have reassured the public that it has taken every possible security precaution, which includes deploying tens of thousands of security personnel.\", \"from\": 2806, \"to\": 3027, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2863, \"end\": 2869, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"score\": 0.7806272156775308, \"rank\": 0.24964949610658882, \"text\": \"French\", \"types\": [\"Q315\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"With inputs from agencies  Erika Kirk delivered an emotional speech from her late husband's studio, addressing President Trump directly.\", \"from\": 3029, \"to\": 3165, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3056, \"end\": 3061, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Erika_Mann\", \"score\": 0.9999958688039283, \"rank\": 4.12349770171226e-06, \"text\": \"Erika\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/